INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2268,2,'2013-06-08 10:51:53','2013-06-08 14:51:53','<h3></h3>\n<h2>Our Product Selection</h2>\n[caption id=\"attachment_174\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"150\"]<a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-2-bags-e1359479456779.png\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-174\" alt=\"Two of the leather bags we make – deerskin and leather.\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-2-bags-150x150.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em>The Algonquin and Sequoia handbags.</em></span>[/caption]\n\nThese relaxed yet sophisticated handbags offer style and everyday functionality. They are the perfect-size to handle the essentials, such as a phone, small wallet, comb, glasses and lipstick.\n<h3></h3>\nThe size of the bag is perfect for a quick shopping trip. For a longer day, it\'s small and flexible and will easily fit in your briefcase or tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\n\nAll bags are carefully handcrafted and fully lined. They measure approximately 8 inches high and 5-1/2 (20 x 14 cm) inches across and weigh only a few ounces (approx. 85 g). Purse feet and a reinforced bottom allow bag to stand upright. Drawstring closure doubles as a wrist strap.\n\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?attachment_id=109\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-109\">Each style offers something a little different; The Algonquin is a stylish leather bag, the Tahoe is a totally vegan bag, and the Niagara is the perfect bag for a busy bride or a perfect bridesmaids gifts.</a></span></em></strong>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/purses81220120801_0122.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-106\" alt=\"PageLines- purses81220120801_0122.jpg\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/purses81220120801_0122-150x150.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Algonquin</em></strong></span></h3>\nThis relaxed yet sophisticated handbag offers style and everyday functionality. Shown in cream and black leather. The size of this bag is perfect carry on a quick outing or move it from briefcase to tote and keep all your essentials in one place.<br class=\"none\" /><br class=\"none\" />\n<h3><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/purses81220120801_0112.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-107\" alt=\"PageLines- purses81220120801_0112.jpg\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/purses81220120801_0112-150x150.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Sequoia</em></strong></span></h3>\nThis  deerskin bucket bag is just the right size to hold all the essentials. Shown in brown and natural deerskin. You’ve got to feel it to know how buttery soft it is! You are sure to get many comments when you carry this bag.\n<h3 align=\"left\"></h3>\n<h3 align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/brocade-bag2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-2269\" alt=\"Brocade bag\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/brocade-bag2-150x150.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Tahoe</em></strong></span></h3>\n<p align=\"left\">This casual and carefree bag is handy for any outing. Shown in denim and brocade, this bag is nature-friendly, since no animal products are used in its production.</p>\n\n<h3></h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h3><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><em><strong><a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/bridal-bag1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-2142\" alt=\"Bridal Handbag\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/bridal-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Niagara</strong></em></span></h3>\n<p align=\"left\">This bag is perfect for a busy bride. It can hold lip gloss, small sprays, phone, money, feminine items and a handkerchief—all the things a bride needs on her big day. <br class=\"none\" /><br class=\"none\" />Shown in faux silk moiré fabric, adorned with beaded fringe and satin flowers, but this bag can be customized to match any bridal dress.</p>\n\n<address>These bags also make excellent gifts for your bridesmaids and wedding party. Ask us about special requests to match bridal gowns.</address>','westcoast/east handbag styles','','inherit','closed','closed','','193-autosave','','','2013-06-08 10:51:53','2013-06-08 14:51:53','',193,'http://www.westcoast-east.com/193-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
